$ Oracle: Lateral inline views

A → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/select/subquery (or more accuratly an → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/select/subquery#ora-sq-inline-view[inline view])
can be marked with the `lateral` keyword which turns it into a *lateral inline view*.

Lateral inline views were introduced with Oracle 12c.

gh|Oracle-Patterns|/SQL/select/12c/lateral.sql||

